[The global measles situation is very discouraging, particularly in the DRC. It is the children who are most affected by this disease, as well as Ebola. It may be a long time before the children in the DRC are able to live normal lives without the weight of civil unrest, measles, and Ebola on their shoulders. - Mod.LK

